From: John Cox <jc@kynesim.co.uk>
Date: Mon, 9 Mar 2026 15:44:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] hevc_d: Pick the fixes from the latest upstreaming reviews

Does NOT include the clock and IRQ changes.

Signed-off-by: John Cox <jc@kynesim.co.uk>
